description.en: A community developed crypto coin striving for robust privacy, ecosystem fairness, full transparency, secure blockchain, and easy use. Swap was created without a pre-mine, governance fees, or founders rewards. It has a custom 15 second block time and is the first CryptoNote coin using a Cuckoo Cycle variant as PoW algorithm, Cuckaroo29s.
